arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)	
	-- Turn off Boss Waves
	Hydra.ActorDisable(SPAWNER_BOSS)
	
	-- Kill remaining monsters
	for i, actorID in pairs(Hydra.ActorsInGroup("Onyx_Watchtower_BossAds")) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(actorID) then
			Hydra.QActorWait(actorID, Hydra.GetRandomFloat())
			Hydra.QActorKill(actorID)
		end
	end
	
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyComplete(BOSS_ENCOUNTER_LEVEL_AREA);

	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(CONV_VICTORY, idActorKiller)
	
	local tAllPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
     
    for i, idPlayer in ipairs(tAllPlayers) do
        -- Drop the TreasureClass, which contains both "always" and "first time" rewards
        -- The First Time stuff is conditioned by the flag that is set after the drop occurs
        Hydra.TreasureClassDropAtActorForPlayer(idActorKilled, "FirstTimeReward_Stronghold_OnyxWatchtower", idPlayer)
         
        -- Set the variable, to mark that this player has recieved a reward
        Hydra.SetPlayerVariableFlag(idPlayer, "FirstTimeReward_Stronghold_OnyxWatchtower")
		
    end
	Hydra.MusicOverride("Sanctuary_Eastern_Continent", "Music_DrySteppes_Watchtower_Complete")	
end

function Start(idActor, fRange, idActorDetector)
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idActorDetector, true)
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idActorDetector, true)
end

function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)

	if Hydra.ActorGetMonsterFamily(idActorSpawned) == "Bandit" then
		Hydra.ActorSetTeam(idActorSpawned, Hydra.TEAM_MONSTER_0)
	end
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	local tDoorGuard = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorGizmo, "doorGuard")
	for i, idActor in pairs(tDoorGuard) do
		Hydra.ActorEnable(idActor)
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONV_SECRET_DOOR, idActor)
	end
end

function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)
	Hydra.ActorAddToBossEncounter(idActorSpawned)
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idActorSpawned, false)
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idActorSpawned, false)
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	Camps.ClaimCamera(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo);
	Hydra.ClearMusicOverride("Sanctuary_Eastern_Continent")
	-- Normally, we pass idActorGizmo into the ActivateWaypoint function, but because Onyx Watchtower's
	-- Wanderer's Shrine is in a different levelarea than the waypoint, we need to pass in the waypoint actor
	Camps.ActivateWaypoint(ID_WAYPOINT)
end

arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(flGameTime)
	if Hydra.QuestCallbackCountGet(24) > 800 then
		Hydra.EventSend("assassin_spawn")
	end
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	
	if (not Hydra.ActorIsValid(idPlayer)) or (Hydra.ActorGetLevelArea(idPlayer) == "Step_OnyxWatchtower_Ascent") then
		local assassin = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(UNIQUE_AMBUSHER, alt_assassin_spawn, true, 0, 2)
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(assassin) then
			Hydra.ActorAddToGroup(assassin, "OnyxWatchtower_Bandits_Uniques")
		end
		Hydra.Wait(2)
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(assassin) then
			Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONV_ASSASSIN, assassin)
		end
	else
		local assassin = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(UNIQUE_AMBUSHER, idPlayer, true, 6, 8)
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(assassin) then
			Hydra.ActorAddToGroup(assassin, "OnyxWatchtower_Bandits_Uniques")
		end
		Hydra.Wait(2)
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(assassin) then
			Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONV_ASSASSIN, assassin)
		end
	end
end
